7","text":"measurement of other cytokine levels such as interferon\\Ngamma, CXCL9, and interleukin-18; valuable where available","guid":"93VmfvjA2hbiVz_mOT1liQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"67","text":"lumbar puncture if neurologic involvement suspected","guid":"UPOyj44B0eRMeBob1CkblQ","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"67","text":"imaging","guid":"LLH_qwRttmfEPdeubnw79A","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) or computed\\Ntomography (CT) to detect neurologic manifestations","guid":"53984gt3rxQuRMlMyuy_zQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"ultrasound or CT to detect hepatosplenomegaly","guid":"XWcCXbNpo8y03YJMvLQy5Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"59","text":"identify underlying\\Ndisease or trigger include","guid":"CpZWGIntKCXsmIoKNHyzMg","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"EBV infection, herpes virus family such as cytomegalovirus,\\NHIV, and hepatitis B and C, and SARS-CoV-2","guid":"N-S7eoz4WEVT70o83dOslQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"arCiscshWW_Iccr1TzGd4Q","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"Objetivo ","guid":"emE2zzCz96ER1BqzrJqnfQ","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Interrumpir el ciclo de hiperinflamación inhibiendo la proliferación y activación\\Nde las células T con terapias mielosupresoras e inmunosupresoras","guid":"e9KWAdXbaSFaqFSOK5V_5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"Terapia basada en\\Netoposidos y dexametasona","guid":"PMTT8PwGfThQIp1TWMIkVQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Régimen HLH-94","guid":"vYaFjz5R5mOfLpi9aorzWA","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Inicialmente, dexametasona IV 10 mg/m2/día con o sin dosis modificada de etoposida [150 mg/m2 o\\N50-100 mg/m2 una vez por semana]) dependiendo del juicio clínico y la función orgánica en adultos.","guid":"CcVJw4LHNnzPs50Wqn44rQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"Con o sin la adición de inmunoglobulina intravenosa\\N(hasta 1,6 g/kg en dosis divididas durante 2-3 días).","guid":"dsWT0tUX2IyfC-df_IiyPQ","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"82","text":"8 semanas de terapia inicial suelen ir seguidas de la\\Nterapia de continuación como puente hacia el HSCT.","guid":"C2Y_-INEZFlQFTb-z4E0cQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"En el HLH secundario, la continuación de la terapia más\\Nallá de las 8 semanas generalmente no es necesaria.","guid":"sZx8e9yViM6-Uwnbwju-qw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"79","text":"Tratamiento de desencadenantes o\\Nafecciones subyacentes","guid":"rVQz8Ctg6YRbystdsBZ1Tg","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"Infección ","guid":"nbvbIYRV6U9f4X4B-TFONw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Adultos con infección por VEB\\Nu otras infecciones virales","guid":"lkkwjjcbXU8tufvbXcalPg","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Rápido deterioro clínico","guid":"Yj4Dd3NLeDv2eosUa6nZoA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Protocolo HLH-94 modificado","guid":"-MPXJdLuodbJqDTjRDmI8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"La enfermedad no está\\Nprogresando rápidamente","guid":"m-yBDQkdJKMs9Q2yAR8Pqw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Considere corticosteroides con o sin inmunoglobulina\\N(IVIG) con etoposida añadida según sea necesario.","guid":"mIYmiHFPeBUvkN3PrcNNCA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"89","text":"Considere rituximab 375 mg/m2 una vez a la semana\\N2-4 veces para la infección por EBV de células B","guid":"LMMnUkjMULn2mSTcmrBT0Q","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"89","text":"Otros HLH asociados a la infección, como las infecciones intracelulares (tuberculosis,\\Nleishmaniasis o enfermedad rickettsial) pueden responder a tratamientos\\Nantimicrobianos específicos y pueden no requerir un tratamiento similar a la HLH-94","guid":"5ZAssXHmvz6KvXZ8PT2mBQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"88","text":"Malignidad","guid":"Zm7Z2NuU2VBUqpwVSAdBxw","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Tratamientos específicos y específicos para tumores","guid":"qbZ64qS1nPDY4KbUguRz3w","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"Corticosteroides para tratar la inflamación (dexametasona 10 mg/m2/día IV).\\NAlgunos pacientes pueden requerir dosis más altas de corticosteroides.","guid":"Olw_El2_5rdRzHz9C5iF2A","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Si la HLH es altamente activa o existe un\\Nriesgo inminente de daño grave a los órganos","guid":"cGTXlWKx_f3be1gNlue7nA","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Considere el uso de etoposide ajustado a la dosis (50-100 mg/m2 una vez por semana)\\Nantes del tratamiento específico del tumor.","guid":"XF0I_engkLmGZaCE1h7isA","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"El etoposido se puede añadir a los protocolos CHOP (ciclofosfamida, doxorrubicina,\\Nvincristina y prednisona) o a los protocolos similares a CHOP.","guid":"u4PBSSbS7YpPvmQkf8lMQw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"88","text":"Autoinmune","guid":"I8TKERm2P522HBZ5Jx4BjQ","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Dosis alta de corticosteroides (dosis alta de\\Nmetilprednisona de pulso, 1 g/día durante 3-5 días)","guid":"852u5_KnizswrzXakeAz9Q","children":[]}]}]}]}]},"node_count":104,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas","filename":"- Síndrome hematofagocitico","id":"map_100","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"- Síndrome hematofagocitico"}